Class CabinetBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.peterzhu.basestation.dao.bean.CabinetBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Named(value="cabinetBean")
 @ConversationScoped
public class CabinetBean
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Contains all the the fields to represent a Cabinet. This is a managed bean using CDI to interact with the JSF frontend.

    3.0
    Author:
